  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to estimate adherence to treatment in bipolar patients, to
      characterize patients based on adherence degree and to describe the variables linked to poor
      adherence to treatment in real-life practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
